<item>
            <title>[FELIX-457] Incorrect URI generated by obr-plugin:deploy</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-457</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When I tried deploying to a remote repository, the URI generated by the maven-obr-plugin was &apos;./C:/MAVEN_REPO/foo.jar&apos; instead of &apos;./foo.jar&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
I believe this is because the extractFileName method in the PathFile class is using &apos;/&apos; instead of File.seperatorChar because after I replaced that, it worked as expected.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Windows XP, Java 1.6.0_02, Maven 2.0.8, maven-obr-plugin-1.0.0 (release)</environment>
        <key id="12386094">FELIX-457</key>
            <summary>Incorrect URI generated by obr-plugin:deploy</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=21133&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
                                            <priority id="3" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/priorities/major.svg">Major</priority>
                        <status id="6" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/statuses/closed.png" description="The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are not closed can be reopened.">Closed</status>
                    <statusCategory id="3" key="done" colorName="green"/>
